    <item>
      <title>Bofa的Hartnett说，出售S＆amp; P 500 Rally直到贸易战争减少</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/bofa-s-hartnett-says-sell-s-p-500-rally-until-trade-war-abates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据美国银行公司的迈克尔·哈特内特（Michael Hartnett）的说法，投资者应出售S＆amp; P 500指数中的任何集会，直到美联储介入并逐步降低了全球贸易战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/bofa-s-hartnett-says-sell-s-p-500-rally-until-trade-war-abates</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Apr 2025 08:42:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行的Villeroy说</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/eu-mustn-t-follow-trump-on-regulation-ecb-s-villeroy-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲中央银行理事会成员弗朗索瓦·维勒罗伊·德·加尔胡（Francois Villeroy de Galhau）警告说，该集团不得跟随美国进行金融管制，而应该专注于简化其规则以提高竞争力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/eu-mustn-t-follow-trump-on-regulation-ecb-s-villeroy-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Apr 2025 08:38:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国将我们的关税提高到125％，并表示不会更高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/china-raises-tariffs-on-us-goods-to-125-in-retaliation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国通过对所有美国商品的远足职责进行报复，同时称政府的行动为“笑话”，并说这不再认为他们值得匹配。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/china-raises-tariffs-on-us-goods-to-125-in-retaliation</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Apr 2025 08:02:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着中国对美国的关税提高到125％，欧洲股票下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/european-stocks-edge-higher-with-index-set-for-third-weekly-loss</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在两国之间的贸易战争又升级时，中国将美国商品的关税提高到125％之后，欧洲股票与美国期货息息相关。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/european-stocks-edge-higher-with-index-set-for-third-weekly-loss</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Apr 2025 07:21:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈萨克斯坦在关键利率持有之后对全球前景的谨慎表示谨慎</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/kazakhstan-holds-interest-rates-as-crude-slump-buffets-tenge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈萨克斯坦的中央银行上个月出人意料地增加了借贷费用，尽管警告说，如果全球金融市场恶化，则准备就货币政策做出计划外的决定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/kazakhstan-holds-interest-rates-as-crude-slump-buffets-tenge</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Apr 2025 07:06:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特斯拉停止在中国接受从美国进口的模型</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/tesla-china-scraps-order-now-option-for-two-imported-ev-models</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特斯拉公司（Tesla Inc.两者都是从美国进口的；在这些国家在不断升级的贸易战中提高关税之后。]]></description>
